OL,3,CThe Welsh Government promise a billion
OL,4,Cpounds for farmers over three years
OL,6,FOn the first day of the Royal Welsh
OL,7,FShow the new Plaid Cymru Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment will guarantee more than a
OL,9,Fbillion pounds for farmers over the
OL,10,Fnext three years.
OL,12,FThe money, which will be delivered
OL,13,Fthrough the Sustainable Farming
OL,14,FScheme, will be the first "multi
OL,15,Fannual" funding cycle for Welsh
OL,16,Fagriculture since Brexit.
OL,18,FThis commitment ends the ends the year-
OL,19,Fto-year funding model, which will be
OL,20,Fwelcome news for farmers.
OL,26,@vD@[OUwD@GO]
