OL,3,CThe Welsh Government promise a billion
OL,4,Cpounds for farmers over three years
OL,6,FDespite the multi year spending
OL,7,Fpledge, the Welsh Government has not
OL,8,Fannounced additional funding, just a
OL,9,Fguarantee for the next three years.
OL,11,FPlaid Cymru in their 2026 Senedd
OL,12,FManifesto pledged to provide a multi-
OL,13,Fannual budget for the Sustainable
OL,14,FFarming Scheme within their first 100
OL,15,Fdays.
OL,17,FWhat is the Sustainable Farming Scheme?
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
