OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784546294
OL,3,CThe Welsh Government promise a billion
OL,4,Cpounds for farmers over three years
OL,6,FThe Sustainable Farming Scheme (SFS)
OL,7,Fwas announced by the previous Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment. It replaces the old Basic
OL,9,FPayment Scheme (BPS) which is being
OL,10,Fphased out completely by the end of
OL,11,F2028
OL,13,FIt means instead of receiving payments
OL,14,Fon the total amount of land farmers
OL,15,Fown, farmers will be rewarded for
OL,16,Fdelivering specific environmental and
OL,17,Fsustainable outcomes alongside
OL,18,Fproducing food.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
