PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784546294
OL,3,CThe Welsh Government promise a billion
OL,4,Cpounds for farmers over three years
OL,6,FThe Sustainable Farming Scheme is
OL,7,Fbroken down into three main layers;
OL,8,Fthe Universal layer, Optional layer,
OL,9,Fand Collaborative layer.
OL,11,FTo qualify for the baseline payment
OL,12,Ffarmers must complete mandatory core
OL,13,Factions which make up the Universal
OL,14,Flayer. These focus on baseline
OL,15,Fenvironmental care and business
OL,16,Fhealth, such as testing soil health
OL,17,Fand committing to animal welfare
OL,18,Fstandards.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784546294
OL,3,CThe Welsh Government promise a billion
OL,4,Cpounds for farmers over three years
OL,6,FFarmers have the opportunity to
OL,7,Freceive additional funding by
OL,8,Fparticipating in the Optional and
OL,9,FCollaborative layer.
OL,11,FThe Optional layer includes things
OL,12,Flike transitioning to organic farming.
OL,13,FThe Collaborative layer provides
OL,14,Ffunding for neighbouring farms to work
OL,15,Ftogether on large-scale environmental
OL,16,Fissues.
OL,18,FThe commitment delivers #340 million
OL,19,Fper year for three years to March 2030
OL,20,Ffor the Sustainable Farming Scheme.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
