CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784546294
OL,3,CThe Welsh Government promise a billion
OL,4,Cpounds for farmers over three years
OL,6,F#238 million per year will be
OL,7,Fallocated for the Universal layer and
OL,8,F#102 million for delivering the
OL,9,FOptional and Collaborative Layers.
OL,11,FThe Cabinet Minister for Rural
OL,12,FResilience and Sustainability, Llyr
OL,13,FGruffydd said: "Giving farmers only 12
OL,14,Fmonths' line of sight to funding is
OL,15,Fnot sufficient.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
