PN,43307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784546294
OL,3,CThe Welsh Government promise a billion
OL,4,Cpounds for farmers over three years
OL,6,F"We know how hard it is to plan and
OL,7,Fmake business decisions without
OL,8,Fknowing what funding is coming.
OL,9,FFarmers told us loud and clear they
OL,10,Fneed certainty and stability ` and
OL,11,Fthat is exactly what we are
OL,12,Fdelivering."
OL,14,FAlthough the Welsh Government have
OL,15,Fpledged a billion pounds, it will need
OL,16,Fto be approved in the upcoming budget
OL,17,Fin the Autumn.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/8
