CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784546294
OL,3,CThe Welsh Government promise a billion
OL,4,Cpounds for farmers over three years
OL,6,FThe new Plaid Cymru Government face a
OL,7,Fsignificant political hurdle to pass
OL,8,Ftheir budget. This comes after they
OL,9,Flost the 'supplementary budget' in the
OL,10,Ffinal week before the Summer recess.
OL,12,FPlaid Cymru do not have a majority in
OL,13,Fthe Senedd, meaning they will need to
OL,14,Fsuccessfully work with other parties
OL,15,Fto approve new spending plans.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/8
